    Open NPSP Settings                      Bulk Data Processes         Level Assignment Batch
    Click Settings Button                   idPanelLvlAssignBatch       Run Batch
    Wait For Batch To Process               LVL_LevelAssign_BATCH       Completed



    Go To Page                              Details
